\c 19
\s Jonatani anoreverera Dhavhidhi kuna Sauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Sauro wakataura kuna Jonatani mwanakomana wake nekuvaranda vake vese kuti vauraye Dhavhidhi. Asi Jonatani mwanakomana waSauro wakafarira Dhavhidhi kwazvo.
\v 2 Jonatani ndokuzivisa Dhavhidhi achiti: Sauro baba vangu vanotsvaka kukuuraya; naizvozvo zvino, chenjerera hako mangwana, uye ugare pakavanda, uvande.
\v 3 Zvino ini ndichabuda ndokumira parutivi rwababa vangu musango mauri. Zvino ndichataurirana nababa vangu pamusoro pako; uye zvandichaona ndichakuudza.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Jonatani wakataura zvakanaka pamusoro paDhavhidhi kuna Sauro baba vake, ndokuti kwavari: Mambo ngaarege kutadzir muranda wake kurwisa Dhavhidhi, nokuti haana kukutadzirai imwi, uye zvakadaro mabasa ake akarurama zvikuru kwamuri.
\v 5 Nokuti wakaisa upenyu hwake muruoko rwake, ndokuuraya muFirisitia; Jehovha ndokuitira Israeri wese ruponeso rukuru, makaona, uye makafara. Zvino munotadzirirei ropa risina mhosva, kuuraya Dhavhidhi pasine chikonzero?
\v 6 Zvino Sauro wakateerera kuinzwi raJonatani, Sauro ndokupika \add achiti\add*: \add Na\add*Jehovha mupenyu, haangaurawi.
\v 7 Zvino Jonatani wakadana Dhavhidhi, Jonatani ndokumuzivisa mashoko ese awa. Jonatani ndokuunza Dhavhidhi kuna Sauro, zvino akava pamberi pake sazuro namarimwezuro.
\s Sauro anoedzazve kuuraya Dhavhidhi
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakavazve nehondo, Dhavhidhi ndokubuda ndokurwa neVaFirisitia. Zvino wakavarova nekurova kukuru kusvika vatiza pachiso chake.
\v 9 Zvino Mweya wakaipa waJehovha wakava pamusoro paSauro agerewo mumba make, uye pfumo rake riri muruoko rwake; Dhavhidhi ndokuridza neruoko rwake.
\v 10 Zvino Sauro wakatsvaka kubaira Dhavhidhi nemumadziro nepfumo; asi wakapukunyuka pakuvonekwa naSauro, iye ndokubaira pfumo nemumadziro, Dhavhidhi ndokutiza, ndokupukunyuka usiku uhwo.
\v 11 Zvino Sauro wakatuma nhume kumba kwaDhavhidhi kumurinda nekumuuraya mangwanani; Mikari mukadzi wake ndokuzivisa kuna Dhavhidhi achiti: Kana ukasaponesa upenyu hwako usiku huno, uchaurawa mangwana.
\p
\v 12 Naizvozvo Mikari akaburutsa Dhavhidhi nepahwindo; zvino akaenda, ndokutiza, ndokupukunyuka.
\v 13 Zvino Mikari wakatora chifananidzo ndokuisa pamubhedha, ndokuisa mutsago wemvere dzembudzi panzvimbo yemusoro wacho, ndokufukidza nemucheka.
\v 14 Zvino Sauro paakatuma nhume kutora Dhavhidhi, iye ndokuti: Anorwara.
\v 15 Sauro ndokutuma\add zve\add* nhume kuzoona Dhavhidhi achiti: Mukwidzei kwandiri ari mumubhedha kuti ndimuuraye.
\v 16 Zvino nhume padzakapinda, zvino tarira, chifananidzo chiri mumubhedha uye mutsago wemvere dzembudzi panzvimbo yemusoro wacho.
\v 17 Zvino Sauro wakati kuna Mikari: Wandinyengedzerei kudai, ndokurega muvengi wangu achienda, zvino wapukunyuka? Mikari ndokuti kuna Sauro: Iye wakati kwandiri: Ndirege ndiende; ndichakuurayirei?
\p
\v 18 Saizvozvo Dhavhidhi wakatiza, ndokupukunyuka, ndokusvika kuna Samueri kuRama, ndokumuzivisa zvese Sauro zvaakaita kwaari. Zvino iye naSamueri ndokuenda kunogara paNaioti.
\v 19 Zvino zvakaziviswa kuna zvichinzi: Tarirai, Dhavhidhi uri paNaioti paRama.
\v 20 Sauro ndokutuma nhume kunotora Dhavhidhi; zvino pavakaona boka revaporofita vachiporofita, naSamueri amire ari mutungamiriri pamusoro pavo, Mweya waMwari ndokuva pamusoro penhume dzaSauro, zvino vakaporofita naivowo.
\v 21 Zvino pakaudzwa Sauro, wakatuma dzimwe nhume, naidzo dzikaporofita saizvozvo. Zvino Sauro wakatumazve nhume rwechitatu, naidzo dzikaporofitawo.
\v 22 Naiye wakaendawo kuRama, ndokusvika patsime guru riri paSeku, ndokubvunza ndokuti: Vana Samueri naDhavhidhi varipi? Zvikanzi: Tarirai, paNaioti paRama.
\v 23 Zvino wakaendako kuNaioti muRama, zvino Mweya waMwari wakava pamusoro pakewo, akafamba achifamba achiporofita kusvika asvika paNaioti muRama.
\v 24 Naiyewo wakakurura nguvo dzake, naiye wakaporofita pamberi paSamueri, ndokurara pasi akashama zuva iro rese neusiku ihwo hwese. Saka vachiti: Sauro naiye ari pakati pevaporofita here?